      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Andreas Herrmann</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:322px;\"><a href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery16.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c2/Herrma13.jpg/320px-Herrma13.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"262\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c2/Herrma13.jpg/480px-Herrma13.jpg 1.5x, /images/c/c2/Herrma13.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Herrma13.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Andreas Herrmann and <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>, <a href=\"/ICT_2002\" title=\"ICT 2002\">ICT 2002</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Andreas Herrmann</b>,<br />\na German software developer and computer chess programmer. He is author of the chess engines <a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessFiz&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ChessFiz (page does not exist)\">ChessFiz</a>, <a href=\"/Holmes\" title=\"Holmes\">Holmes</a> and <a href=\"/BlackBishop\" title=\"BlackBishop\">BlackBishop</a>, all written in <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Herrmann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Herrmann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=129406\">A question about pawn hash tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 13, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=154398\">Depth in Hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=184473\">Movegenerator with Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=36446\">Which is the strongest Delphi chess program?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, March 14, 2002 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=217882\">Which is the strongest Delphi chess program?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 14, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=266390\">Attack tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 20, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Attack_and_Defend_Maps\" title=\"Attack and Defend Maps\">Attack and Defend Maps</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=271760\">correct SAN notation&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 19, 2002&#160;»  <a href=\"/Algebraic_Chess_Notation#SAN\" title=\"Algebraic Chess Notation\">Standard Algebraic Notation (SAN)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=41318\">Perft</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 18, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=293853\">Counting bits</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 17, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Population_Count\" title=\"Population Count\">Population Count</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=345832\">perpetual check recognition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  January 30, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Herrmann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=5825\">BlackBishop 0.35</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 04, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=5864\">BlackBishop 0.470</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>,  November 13, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=50192&amp;p=190067\">Engines written in which programming language?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 01, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=50203\">BlackBishop 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andreas Herrmann</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 07, 2009</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Herrmann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20031224014149/http:/www.wbholmes.de/links_pascal.htm\">Links for Pascal/Delphi chess programmers</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andreas_Herrmann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://old.csvn.nl/gallery16.html\">2nd International CSVN Tournament (2002)</a> - Photo Gallery I</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CodeGear_Delphi\">CodeGear Delphi from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301131104\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6363-0!canonic